description: They are accused of targeting the high-tech sector and building a "substantial network of sources".
title: Netherlands expels two Russians after uncovering 'espionage network'
title_page: Netherlands expels two Russians after uncovering 'espionage network' - BBC News
maintext: The announcement comes a day after the European Medicines Agency (EMA), which has its headquarters in Amsterdam, said it had been hit by a cyber-attack. There is, however, no indication that the incidents are linked.
